<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink320">
<l>muḷḷarai yilavat toḷḷiṇar vāṉpū</l>
<l>muḻaṅkaḻa lacaivaḷi yeṭuppa vāṉat</l>
<l>turumuppaṭu kaṉali ṉirunilat tuṟaikkuṅ</l>
<l>kavalai yaruñcuram pōyiṉar</l>
<l>tavali larunōy talaittan tōrē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>He has given me this rare disease which will not go away - </l>
<l>the man who left for the the difficult desert with [dangerous] crossroads, </l>
<l>where beautiful flowers from the bright clusters</l> 
<l>of the Silk-cotton trees with thorny trunks,</l> 
<l>when fitful wind disperses them like crackling sparks,</l>
<l>fall down the vast land, like lightning from the sky accompanied by thunder.</l>
    </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
